cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.IR 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with language models and discourse structure. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it uses recurrent neural networks. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it deals with natural language processing and language generation. It may also be relevant to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it uses neural networks, and cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it deals with document coherence.
